TITLE: Episode 27 - Silicon Valley Myths and COVID-19's Impact on Tech
DESCRIPTION: In this episode, Thaddeus and Gary discuss the effects of COVID-19 on the tech world, people's changing opinions of Silicon Valley, and the myth of cloud energy consumption.
